paragraphs.title: Where do we need to improve?
paragraphs.text:
select A.Highly_Rated,B.Number_of_Offices,A.state from (select count(*) as Highly_Rated,state from amerredcrossheadq where score>90 group by state order by Highly_Rated desc) A INNER JOIN 
(select count(*) as Number_of_Offices,state from amerredcrossheadq group by state order by Number_of_Offices desc) B on A.state=B.state where A.state = decode( '${STATE}','All', A.state, '${STATE=All,All|AL|AK|AZ|AR|CA|CO|CT|DE|FL|GA|HI|ID|IL|IN|IA|KS|KY|LA|ME|MD|MA|MI|MN|MS|MO|MT|NE|NV|NH|NJ|NM|NY|NC|ND|OH|OK|OR|PA|RI| SC|SD|TN|TX|UT|VT|VA|WA|WV|WI|WY|AS|DC|FM|GU|MH|MP|PW|PR|VI}' );
